<h3 class="text-3xl mb-8">Feeding back to peers can be hard, but development leads to better outcomes for all</h3>
<p class="text-lg mb-8">As you're a peer, and especially if you're working in a team together, you may be thinking that relationship building trumps feedback - and that giving feedback will create barriers that make life more difficult. Resist these urges - remind yourself and them that development leads to better outcomes for all of us - and that you hope you can both learn from having what seems to be an uncomfortable conversation</p>
